1
00:00:10,100 --> 00:00:10,900
Come here.

2
00:00:16,230 --> 00:00:19,690
Did the Grand Tutor teach you to serve your master standing up?

3
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:23,400
I will help the General change clothes.

4
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:31,700
You are really obedient.

5
00:00:32,159 --> 00:00:34,000
Doing whatever you are told.

6
00:00:38,830 --> 00:00:41,290
It's a pity that I despise this face of yours.

7
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:42,830
I have no interest at all.

8
00:00:43,230 --> 00:00:44,830
If I cannot succeed tonight,

9
00:00:45,030 --> 00:00:47,500
the Grand Tutor's mansion will send someone else for the trial marriage tomorrow.

10
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:49,430
Then my plan will be completely ruined.

11
00:00:49,430 --> 00:00:52,060
No, the medicine seems to be taking effect.

12
00:00:53,460 --> 00:00:55,800
Lu Jingxing, is this all you've got?

13
00:00:58,430 --> 00:00:59,360
What did you say?

14
00:01:00,230 --> 00:01:02,730
I used to be your master, the Eldest Lady.

15
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:05,730
You served me as if I were a deity.

16
00:01:05,860 --> 00:01:08,660
Now you are a high and mighty General,

17
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:11,220
but you still don't dare to lay a finger on me?

18
00:01:22,630 --> 00:01:23,400
Hyah!

19
00:01:24,130 --> 00:01:24,900
Hyah!

20
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:30,360
Shen Lvyi,

21
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:32,100
I advise you not to court death.

22
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:33,100
Come on.

23
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:34,860
When scholars are apart for three days,

24
00:01:34,860 --> 00:01:36,500
they must look at each other with new eyes.

25
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:39,759
Lu Jingxing, let me see what you are capable of now.

26
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:47,660
Shen Lvyi,

27
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,160
you asked for this.

28
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:05,690
It's been three years.

29
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:08,259
I haven't slept so soundly.

30
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,160
Does the General want me to help you wash up?

31
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:14,960
No need.

32
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,460
It's still early, sleep a little longer.

33
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,300
Three years ago, the late Emperor passed away.

34
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:29,400
The current Emperor ascended the throne.

35
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,130
The Minister's mansion was raided overnight.

36
00:02:31,130 --> 00:02:32,660
Minister Shen was thrown into death row.

37
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:34,000
The male members of the household were exiled.

38
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,430
And the female members were made slaves.

39
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,260
The Eldest Lady Shen begged the Second Lady Wei.

40
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:39,530
The Grand Tutor's mansion bought the Shen family's female members.

41
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:40,800
Wei the Second is narrow-minded and vicious.

42
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:43,860
When they were young, she and the Eldest Lady were secretly at odds.

43
00:02:43,860 --> 00:02:45,660
With the Eldest Lady's intelligence and resourcefulness,

44
00:02:45,660 --> 00:02:47,760
it stands to reason she wouldn't beg the Wei family for shelter.

45
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:48,960
The Second Lady Wei offered help in their hour of need.

46
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,930
So kind of her.

47
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,530
With such a virtuous wife, General,

48
00:02:51,530 --> 00:02:53,560
you two will surely have a harmonious marriage.

49
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,630
Kind my ass.

50
00:02:54,930 --> 00:02:56,800
I don't want to marry a vulgar woman like her.

51
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,930
Last year, His Majesty wanted to marry his legitimate princess to you.

52
00:02:58,930 --> 00:03:00,400
You also said the Princess was vulgar.

53
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,660
In the General's eyes,

54
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:03,390
what kind of girl is not vulgar?

55
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,500
Cut the crap.

56
00:03:05,130 --> 00:03:07,930
Which month was the Minister's mansion raided three years ago?

57
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:08,730
June.

58
00:03:08,900 --> 00:03:10,430
She dealt with me in April.

59
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,360
As soon as I left, the Minister's mansion fell.

60
00:03:13,460 --> 00:03:15,660
Could there be a hidden truth I don't know about?

61
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:18,320
General, the things you asked for are all ready.

62
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:22,430
I wanted Yunjin and Shu brocade.

63
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,020
This is ordinary brocade.

64
00:03:24,060 --> 00:03:26,730
For rouge, I wanted the rose paste tributed from Jiangnan.

65
00:03:26,730 --> 00:03:28,800
The face powder must be ground from pearls.

66
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,800
Such cheap cosmetics.

67
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,829
How can she use them?

68
00:03:30,829 --> 00:03:31,730
Why can't she?

69
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,900
These are all trendy goods bought with a lot of money.

70
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,500
Who told you to buy them on the street?

71
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:37,800
Didn't His Majesty reward me with several storehouses of treasures?

72
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,660
Pick the best ones from there for her.

73
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:41,000
Those are imperial gifts.

74
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,030
How can a trial marriage maid use them?

75
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,430
Although she is of low status,

76
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,660
she is my woman after all.

77
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:46,660
If she doesn't eat and dress well,

78
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:48,320
it makes me look incompetent.

79
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:49,760
What you say makes sense, General.

80
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,730
Go ahead and pick some more.

81
00:03:51,930 --> 00:03:53,860
Let her see what I'm capable of now.

82
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,360
When you give them to her,

83
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,200
watch her expression carefully,

84
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,930
and report back to me in detail.

85
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:12,330
Marks are located on the sides of the neck, collarbone, and waist.

86
00:04:12,330 --> 00:04:14,760
The General favors beautiful necks and slender waists.

87
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,660
Got it, Madam Zhang.

88
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:17,730
For this first night,

89
00:04:17,730 --> 00:04:19,130
everything has been recorded.

90
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,930
Let Miss Shen put her clothes on.

91
00:04:20,930 --> 00:04:22,060
Who said we're done?

92
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:24,300
Go.

93
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,830
Show the poses the General used last night.

94
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,730
Let Madam Li record them carefully,

95
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:30,560
so the Second Miss can see them later.

96
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,030
so she will be clear.

97
00:04:32,030 --> 00:04:33,830
Just now, according to what you asked,

98
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:35,730
I have already described everything in detail.

99
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:37,530
You pushing your luck like this,

100
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:40,020
is nothing more than trying to humiliate me.

101
00:04:40,730 --> 00:04:41,730
Madam Zhang.

102
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,800
It's true I am a slave,

103
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:45,700
but you are a servant too.

104
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:47,400
Why must you make things so difficult for me?

105
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,900
I am a slave born in the Grand Tutor's Mansion.

106
00:04:49,900 --> 00:04:52,830
I am much better than those who sold themselves here like you.

107
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,230
Look at a rat, it has skin;

108
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,820
but a man without dignity,

109
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:57,090
a man without dignity,

110
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,760
what else is there but to die?

111
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,800
Have you heard of this?

112
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,700
What... what rat?

113
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:03,200
It means,

114
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:05,430
if a person willingly degrades themselves,

115
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,830
they are worse than a rat,

116
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,160
and might as well be dead,

117
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,490
rather than gloating like a petty person.

118
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,600
You little wench!

119
00:05:16,130 --> 00:05:17,360
Is Miss Shen there?

120
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,700
We are here to deliver things on the General's orders.

121
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:21,500
Please open the door, Miss Shen.

122
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:24,360
Come in, the door is unlocked.

123
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,420
Get out! Everyone get out!

124
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,100
Look how panicked you are.

125
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:36,330
What a bunch of inexperienced rookies.

126
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,690
You old woman, did you set us up on purpose?

127
00:05:38,700 --> 00:05:40,200
How is this setting you up?

128
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,330
Although she is a lowly slave now,

129
00:05:42,330 --> 00:05:45,860
she used to be the precious Eldest Miss of the Minister's Manor.

130
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,460
With such delicate skin,

131
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:48,760
in the past,

132
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:50,900
you'd never have had the chance to look at her.

133
00:05:50,900 --> 00:05:52,900
The Eldest Miss of the Minister's Manor?

134
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:53,860
Isn't that...

135
00:05:54,659 --> 00:05:56,460
No wonder the General is acting so out of character.
